	   <tr><td colspan=2>After spending 16 RL days at this spawn I finished the quest. <br>I missed three live spawns and two dead spawns so it might not take you as long to do.<br><br>The undead Grimrot was Blue to me at 34th, and a very easy kill. Low HP and MR.<br><br>The live version concidered 3 different levels at three different spawns. White, Yellow and Red. All three very nasty. High HP and MR.<br><br>I can say there is NO logic to the spawns, just kill the PH and go on, I tried killing the PH at all different times, 5am/pm, 12am/pm nothing worked it was random. <br><br>The PH DOESN'T despawn. The PH is under the "tent" in the middle of three gold topped tents, the tent the PH spawns in does not have a gold top. <br><br>The PH is the STANDING putrid skeleton with a rusty Bastard sword. NOT the sitting small putrid skeleton with the bastardsword that spawns.<br><br>I never did anything to messup or improve my faction with the ToL before beginging this quest. I killed about 100 putrid skeletons, got the faction hit for killing 3 live Grimrots, and turned in 100pp to Novashine and that was plenty of faction for the quest.<br><br>Hi to everyone I met doing this quest on the Emarr server.<br><br>Crescentnight Brokensoul<br>34th DE Cleric of Innoruuk<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
